WEBVTT

00:03:58.730 --> 00:04:03.933
pretty much every pandemic
is first viewed with denial and doubt.

00:04:03.957 --> 00:04:05.823
But those countries that acted quickly,

00:04:05.847 --> 00:04:08.471
and even those who started slow,
like South Korea,

00:04:08.495 --> 00:04:11.709
they could still make up for it,
and they did really well.

00:04:12.204 --> 00:04:15.029
We've had two months that we've lost.

00:04:15.053 --> 00:04:18.989
We've given a virus
that moves exponentially

00:04:19.013 --> 00:04:20.918
a two-month head start.

00:04:20.942 --> 00:04:22.942
That's not a good idea, Chris.

00:04:23.387 --> 00:04:24.609
CA: No, indeed.

00:04:24.633 --> 00:04:27.490
I mean, there's so much
puzzling information still out there

00:04:27.514 --> 00:04:29.618
about this virus.

